sensor
-----------
	serial_number
	device_template
	meta_data
		name-value pairs
	+ location: special variable
	+ path : special variable

readings
----------
	sensor.serial_number
	sensor.device.variables
	sensor.device.meta_data
	sensor.meta_data
	+ sensor.special_variables
	+ timestamp
	
	
